728677f-a.title: Richmond: Central Avenue - Hyatt Street
728677f-a.text:
20 to 34 (right to left), Central Ave., west side, between
Hyatt Street and Slosson Terrace. Also shown is a panoramic view
westward of New Brighton as seen from No. 30 Bay Street.
April 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
